{"tid":740981,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA公開讚哥迪奧拿　「Pep效應」改善比賽質素","createTime":"2018-07-13T09:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T08:39:04.000Z","uid":153341,"like":24,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa270fa21cf7c7a9f576184a583c7fe9a5742fc","tid":740981,"uid":153341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"今屆世界盃多場比賽精彩刺激，哥迪奧拿都有功勞？根據國際足協（FIFA）的技術委員會，這名曼城領隊確實應記一功；其中一名成員洛斯保（Andy Roxburgh），盛讚哥帥式控傳戰術使賽事變得更精彩。<br />\n<br />\n曾執教蘇格蘭國家隊的洛斯保，大讚哥帥改變了現今足球形態：「明顯地，哥迪奧拿對很多球員及教練都有很大的影響，『Pep效應』雖仍是高控球風格，但並非為控球率而持球，那是種滲透力超強的風格。」<br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿今季帶領曼城強勢奪得英超冠軍，創下單季最高積分（100分）、最高入球（106球）、最多連勝（18場）紀錄，雖然歐聯8強不敵利物浦出局，但哥帥的曼城仍被視為歐洲最強之一。"},{"pid":"3713643f9f2da78893ef86a03f57741459bc38f9","tid":740981,"uid":29993,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"我利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098f2d806cc0ca7db544d54bbe5241b2cd92ee71","tid":740981,"uid":161311,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"哥狗不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb44c33bd25f80a44bb972122082fc19fa2f7033","tid":740981,"uid":128014,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"佢班正選球員裡面除咗廸布尼、甘賓尼同石頭，無個踢得勁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b647849e2a0b53d5a783fda2a3dfcaac4d473be6","tid":740981,"uid":70013,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:40:42.000Z","msg":"世界盃有邊隊係咁踢"},{"pid":"6fb3ae2ed06d8db7bb12992c8423d748a81d15a1","tid":740981,"uid":28,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"世盃西班牙睇到訓著"},{"pid":"8c141d52e2be09ba66a52e5c11d02079154339be","tid":740981,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:42:34.000Z","m